    <entry>
      <title>数据结构总统筹学习</title>
      <link href="/2026/05/27/d12db421/"/>
      <url>/2026/05/27/d12db421/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="数据结构总统筹学习"><a href="#数据结构总统筹学习" class="headerlink" title="数据结构总统筹学习"></a>数据结构总统筹学习</h1><blockquote><p>本文档系统梳理 C 语言视角下的核心数据结构，从动态内存分配到复杂树结构，构建完整知识体系。</p></blockquote><hr><h2 id="01-Dynamic-Memory-Allocation"><a href="#01-Dynamic-Memory-Allocation" class="headerlink" title="01 &#x2F; Dynamic Memory Allocation"></a>01 &#x2F; Dynamic Memory Allocation</h2><p>在学习复杂的数据结构之前，需要改变创建固定大小数组的思维定式，引入<strong>动态内存分配</strong>。</p><div class="note info flat"><p><strong>Core Concept</strong>：数组分配内存在栈（stack）中，动态分配的内存位于堆（Heap）中，需要手动调用 <code>free(p)</code> 释放，释放后建议将指针置为 <code>p = NULL</code> 以避免野指针。</p></div><h3 id="三个核心函数"><a href="#三个核心函数" class="headerlink" title="三个核心函数"></a>三个核心函数</h3><table><thead><tr><th>函数</th><th>用途</th><th>示例</th><th>特性</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>malloc</code></td><td>分配内存</td><td><code>int* p = (int*)malloc(10 * sizeof(int))</code></td><td>内容随机，不初始化</td></tr><tr><td><code>calloc</code></td><td>分配并清零</td><td><code>int* p = (int*)calloc(10, sizeof(int))</code></td><td>自动初始化为 0</td></tr><tr><td><code>realloc</code></td><td>调整内存大小</td><td><code>p = (int*)realloc(p, 20 * sizeof(int))</code></td><td>可扩容 &#x2F; 缩容</td></tr></tbody></table><hr><h2 id="02-Sequential-List"><a href="#02-Sequential-List" class="headerlink" title="02 &#x2F; Sequential List"></a>02 &#x2F; Sequential List</h2><p>数组的增强版，保留随机访问优势，同时提供动态扩容能力。</p><h3 id="结构体定义"><a href="#结构体定义" class="headerlink" title="结构体定义"></a>结构体定义</h3><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> *data;      <span class="comment">// 指向堆内存</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> length;     <span class="comment">// 当前元素数量</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> capacity;   <span class="comment">// 最大存储量</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125; SeqList;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="基本操作"><a href="#基本操作" class="headerlink" title="基本操作"></a>基本操作</h3><table><thead><tr><th>操作</th><th>函数名</th><th>时间复杂度</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>初始化</td><td>Init</td><td>O(1)</td><td>分配内存，设置初始值</td></tr><tr><td>插入</td><td>Insert</td><td>O(n)</td><td>在指定位置插入元素</td></tr><tr><td>删除</td><td>Delete</td><td>O(n)</td><td>删除指定位置的元素</td></tr><tr><td>按位查找</td><td>GetByPos</td><td>O(1)</td><td>通过下标直接访问</td></tr><tr><td>按值查找</td><td>FindByVal</td><td>O(n)</td><td>遍历查找第一个匹配项</td></tr><tr><td>修改</td><td>Update</td><td>O(1)</td><td>修改指定位置的值</td></tr><tr><td>销毁</td><td>Destroy</td><td>O(1)</td><td>释放内存</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="适用场景分析"><a href="#适用场景分析" class="headerlink" title="适用场景分析"></a>适用场景分析</h3><table><thead><tr><th>场景</th><th>原因</th><th>实例</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>频繁按位置访问</td><td>O(1) 随机访问</td><td>成绩单、排行榜</td></tr><tr><td>数据量相对固定</td><td>一次分配，无需扩容</td><td>月份天数、星期</td></tr><tr><td>尾部增删为主</td><td>尾部操作不需移动</td><td>日志记录、消息队列</td></tr><tr><td>存储密集型</td><td>空间利用率高（无指针）</td><td>图像像素、音频采样</td></tr><tr><td>排序后数据</td><td>二分查找需要 O(1) 访问</td><td>电话本、字典</td></tr></tbody></table><hr><h2 id="03-Linked-List"><a href="#03-Linked-List" class="headerlink" title="03 &#x2F; Linked List"></a>03 &#x2F; Linked List</h2><p>指针串起的动态结构，牺牲随机访问速度，换取 O(1) 的插入删除。</p><h3 id="结构体定义-1"><a href="#结构体定义-1" class="headerlink" title="结构体定义"></a>结构体定义</h3><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">Node</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> data;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">Node</span>* <span class="title">next</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125; Node;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    Node* head;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> length;</span><br><span class="line">&#125; LinkedList;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="基本操作-1"><a href="#基本操作-1" class="headerlink" title="基本操作"></a>基本操作</h3><table><thead><tr><th>操作</th><th>函数名</th><th>时间复杂度</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>初始化</td><td>InitList</td><td>O(1)</td><td>创建头结点</td></tr><tr><td>头插法</td><td>InsertHead</td><td>O(1)</td><td>在头部插入</td></tr><tr><td>尾插法</td><td>InsertTail</td><td>O(1)*</td><td>需尾指针</td></tr><tr><td>指定位置插入</td><td>Insert</td><td>O(n)</td><td>遍历到 pos-1</td></tr><tr><td>头删</td><td>DeleteHead</td><td>O(1)</td><td>删除第一个结点</td></tr><tr><td>尾删</td><td>DeleteTail</td><td>O(n)</td><td>遍历到倒数第二个</td></tr><tr><td>指定位置删除</td><td>Delete</td><td>O(n)</td><td>遍历到 pos-1</td></tr><tr><td>按位查找</td><td>Get</td><td>O(n)</td><td>遍历到第 i 个</td></tr><tr><td>按值查找</td><td>Find</td><td>O(n)</td><td>遍历直到找到</td></tr><tr><td>销毁</td><td>DestroyList</td><td>O(n)</td><td>逐个释放结点</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="note danger flat"><p><strong>注</strong>：尾插 O(1) 的前提是链表持有 <code>tail</code> 指针。</p></div><h3 id="链表的变体"><a href="#链表的变体" class="headerlink" title="链表的变体"></a>链表的变体</h3><table><thead><tr><th>类型</th><th>结构特点</th><th>适用场景</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>单向链表</td><td>只有 next 指针</td><td>大多数场景</td></tr><tr><td>双向链表</td><td>prev + next</td><td>反向遍历、O(1) 删除指定结点</td></tr><tr><td>循环链表</td><td>尾结点指向头结点</td><td>约瑟夫环、轮询调度</td></tr><tr><td>静态链表</td><td>数组模拟</td><td>不支持指针的低级环境</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="适用场景分析-1"><a href="#适用场景分析-1" class="headerlink" title="适用场景分析"></a>适用场景分析</h3><table><thead><tr><th>场景</th><th>原因</th><th>实例</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>频繁插入&#x2F;删除</td><td>O(1) 时间，不移动元素</td><td>任务调度、消息队列</td></tr><tr><td>数据量不确定</td><td>按需分配，无容量概念</td><td>动态数据采集</td></tr><tr><td>内存碎片化</td><td>不需要连续大块内存</td><td>嵌入式系统</td></tr><tr><td>多项式运算</td><td>稀疏存储非零项</td><td>科学计算</td></tr><tr><td>LRU 缓存</td><td>移动结点到头部 O(1)</td><td>Redis、浏览器缓存</td></tr></tbody></table><hr><h2 id="04-Stack"><a href="#04-Stack" class="headerlink" title="04 &#x2F; Stack"></a>04 &#x2F; Stack</h2><p>后进先出（LIFO），只能在栈顶操作是其本质特征。</p><h3 id="顺序栈结构体定义"><a href="#顺序栈结构体定义" class="headerlink" title="顺序栈结构体定义"></a>顺序栈结构体定义</h3><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span>* data;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> top;        <span class="comment">// 栈顶元素下标</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> capacity;</span><br><span class="line">&#125; Stack;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="核心操作"><a href="#核心操作" class="headerlink" title="核心操作"></a>核心操作</h3><table><thead><tr><th>操作</th><th>函数名</th><th>时间复杂度</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>入栈</td><td>Push</td><td>O(1)</td><td>压入栈顶</td></tr><tr><td>出栈</td><td>Pop</td><td>O(1)</td><td>弹出栈顶</td></tr><tr><td>查看栈顶</td><td>GetTop &#x2F; Peek</td><td>O(1)</td><td>只读不删</td></tr><tr><td>判空</td><td>IsEmpty</td><td>O(1)</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>获取大小</td><td>GetSize</td><td>O(1)</td><td>-</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="适用场景分析-2"><a href="#适用场景分析-2" class="headerlink" title="适用场景分析"></a>适用场景分析</h3><table><thead><tr><th>场景</th><th>原理</th><th>实例</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>函数调用</td><td>后调用先返回</td><td>递归、嵌套调用</td></tr><tr><td>括号匹配</td><td>左括号入栈，右括号出栈配对</td><td>编译器语法检查</td></tr><tr><td>表达式求值</td><td>运算符优先级处理</td><td>计算器程序</td></tr><tr><td>撤销操作</td><td>后做操作先撤销</td><td>Ctrl+Z</td></tr><tr><td>浏览历史</td><td>后退回到上一页面</td><td>浏览器前进后退</td></tr><tr><td>DFS</td><td>回溯机制</td><td>迷宫求解</td></tr><tr><td>表达式转换</td><td>中缀转后缀</td><td>编译器优化</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="实战案例：括号匹配"><a href="#实战案例：括号匹配" class="headerlink" title="实战案例：括号匹配"></a>实战案例：括号匹配</h3><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span> <span class="string">&lt;stdbool.h&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">bool</span> <span class="title function_">IsValidParentheses</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">char</span> *s)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    Stack S;</span><br><span class="line">    InitStack(&amp;S);</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; s[i] != <span class="string">&#x27;\0&#x27;</span>; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (s[i] == <span class="string">&#x27;(&#x27;</span> || s[i] == <span class="string">&#x27;[&#x27;</span> || s[i] == <span class="string">&#x27;&#123;&#x27;</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            Push(&amp;S, s[i]);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (IsEmpty(&amp;S)) <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">int</span> top = GetTop(&amp;S);</span><br><span class="line">            Pop(&amp;S, &amp;top);</span><br><span class="line">            </span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (s[i] == <span class="string">&#x27;)&#x27;</span> &amp;&amp; top != <span class="string">&#x27;(&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (s[i] == <span class="string">&#x27;]&#x27;</span> &amp;&amp; top != <span class="string">&#x27;[&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (s[i] == <span class="string">&#x27;&#125;&#x27;</span> &amp;&amp; top != <span class="string">&#x27;&#123;&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">bool</span> result = IsEmpty(&amp;S);</span><br><span class="line">    DestroyStack(&amp;S);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> result;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h2 id="05-Queue"><a href="#05-Queue" class="headerlink" title="05 &#x2F; Queue"></a>05 &#x2F; Queue</h2><p>先进先出（FIFO）。</p><h3 id="循环队列结构体定义"><a href="#循环队列结构体定义" class="headerlink" title="循环队列结构体定义"></a>循环队列结构体定义</h3><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span>* data;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> front;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> rear;       <span class="comment">// 指向队尾下一个空位</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> capacity;   <span class="comment">// 实际可用 capacity-1 个元素</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125; Queue;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note warning flat"><p><strong>Note</strong>：循环队列扩容不能直接使用 <code>realloc</code>，因元素在数组中不连续。需 <code>malloc</code> 新内存后手动复制。</p></div><h3 id="扩容实现"><a href="#扩容实现" class="headerlink" title="扩容实现"></a>扩容实现</h3><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">Expand</span><span class="params">(Queue* Q)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> newCapacity = Q-&gt;capacity * <span class="number">2</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span>* newData = (<span class="type">int</span>*)<span class="built_in">malloc</span>(newCapacity * <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(<span class="type">int</span>));</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> size = (Q-&gt;rear - Q-&gt;front + Q-&gt;capacity) % Q-&gt;capacity;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; size; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        newData[i] = Q-&gt;data[(Q-&gt;front + i) % Q-&gt;capacity];</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">free</span>(Q-&gt;data);</span><br><span class="line">    Q-&gt;data = newData;</span><br><span class="line">    Q-&gt;front = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    Q-&gt;rear = size;</span><br><span class="line">    Q-&gt;capacity = newCapacity;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="核心操作-1"><a href="#核心操作-1" class="headerlink" title="核心操作"></a>核心操作</h3><table><thead><tr><th>操作</th><th>函数名</th><th>时间复杂度</th><th>循环队列特有条件</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>初始化</td><td>InitQueue</td><td>O(1)</td><td>front &#x3D; rear &#x3D; 0</td></tr><tr><td>入队</td><td>Enqueue</td><td>O(1) 均摊</td><td>rear &#x3D; (rear+1) % capacity</td></tr><tr><td>出队</td><td>Dequeue</td><td>O(1)</td><td>front &#x3D; (front+1) % capacity</td></tr><tr><td>判空</td><td>IsEmpty</td><td>O(1)</td><td>front &#x3D;&#x3D; rear</td></tr><tr><td>判满</td><td>IsFull</td><td>O(1)</td><td>(rear+1) % capacity &#x3D;&#x3D; front</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="适用场景分析-3"><a href="#适用场景分析-3" class="headerlink" title="适用场景分析"></a>适用场景分析</h3><table><thead><tr><th>场景</th><th>原因</th><th>实例</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>固定大小缓冲区</td><td>环形复用，不扩容</td><td>串口缓冲、音频缓冲</td></tr><tr><td>生产者-消费者模型</td><td>一写一读，环形同步</td><td>多线程任务队列</td></tr><tr><td>滑动窗口</td><td>窗口固定大小</td><td>网络流量统计</td></tr><tr><td>最近 N 条记录</td><td>只保留最新</td><td>游戏 Replay、日志缓存</td></tr><tr><td>嵌入式系统</td><td>内存受限</td><td>单片机数据采集</td></tr></tbody></table><hr><h2 id="06-String"><a href="#06-String" class="headerlink" title="06 &#x2F; String"></a>06 &#x2F; String</h2><p>增强版字符串，封装长度字段与二进制安全存储。</p><h3 id="char-vs-Struct-String"><a href="#char-vs-Struct-String" class="headerlink" title="char[] vs Struct String"></a>char[] vs Struct String</h3><table><thead><tr><th>能力</th><th>char[]</th><th>Struct String</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>O(1) 获取长度</td><td>❌</td><td>✅</td></tr><tr><td>存储二进制</td><td>❌ 遇 \0 终止</td><td>✅</td></tr><tr><td>零拷贝取子串</td><td>❌</td><td>✅</td></tr><tr><td>自动扩容</td><td>❌</td><td>✅</td></tr><tr><td>C 库兼容</td><td>✅</td><td>需转换</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="结构体定义-2"><a href="#结构体定义-2" class="headerlink" title="结构体定义"></a>结构体定义</h3><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">char</span>* data;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> length;</span><br><span class="line">&#125; MyString;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="核心操作-2"><a href="#核心操作-2" class="headerlink" title="核心操作"></a>核心操作</h3><table><thead><tr><th>操作</th><th>函数名</th><th>时间复杂度</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>赋值</td><td>StrAssign</td><td>O(n)</td></tr><tr><td>复制</td><td>StrCopy</td><td>O(n)</td></tr><tr><td>判空</td><td>StrEmpty</td><td>O(1)</td></tr><tr><td>比较</td><td>StrCompare</td><td>O(n)</td></tr><tr><td>求长</td><td>StrLength</td><td>O(1)</td></tr><tr><td>拼接</td><td>Concat</td><td>O(n+m)</td></tr><tr><td>取子串</td><td>SubString</td><td>O(n)</td></tr><tr><td>定位</td><td>Index</td><td>O(n×m)</td></tr><tr><td>插入</td><td>StrInsert</td><td>O(n)</td></tr><tr><td>删除</td><td>StrDelete</td><td>O(n)</td></tr><tr><td>替换</td><td>Replace</td><td>O(n×m)</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="应用场景"><a href="#应用场景" class="headerlink" title="应用场景"></a>应用场景</h3><table><thead><tr><th>场景</th><th>实例</th><th>关键操作</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>文本编辑器</td><td>Ctrl+F</td><td>查找、替换</td></tr><tr><td>搜索引擎</td><td>关键词搜索</td><td>KMP 匹配</td></tr><tr><td>编译器</td><td>词法分析</td><td>模式匹配</td></tr><tr><td>DNA 分析</td><td>基因匹配</td><td>最长公共子串</td></tr><tr><td>数据压缩</td><td>LZ77</td><td>查找重复子串</td></tr><tr><td>NLP</td><td>分词</td><td>分割、匹配</td></tr></tbody></table><hr><h2 id="07-Huffman-Tree"><a href="#07-Huffman-Tree" class="headerlink" title="07 &#x2F; Huffman Tree"></a>07 &#x2F; Huffman Tree</h2><p>带权路径长度最短的二叉树，即最优二叉树。</p><h3 id="结构体定义-3"><a href="#结构体定义-3" class="headerlink" title="结构体定义"></a>结构体定义</h3><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> weight;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> parent;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> left;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> right;      <span class="comment">// -1 表示无</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125; HuffNode;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">char</span> ch;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">char</span> code[MAX_SIZE];</span><br><span class="line">&#125; HuffCode;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="生成编码"><a href="#生成编码" class="headerlink" title="生成编码"></a>生成编码</h3><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="type">void</span> <span class="title function_">GenerateCodes</span><span class="params">(HuffNode* nodes, HuffCode* codes, <span class="type">int</span> n)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">char</span> temp[MAX_SIZE];</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> i = <span class="number">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> idx = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> child = i;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="type">int</span> parent = nodes[child].parent;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span> (parent != <span class="number">-1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">if</span> (nodes[parent].left == child) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                temp[idx++] = <span class="string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125; <span class="keyword">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">                temp[idx++] = <span class="string">&#x27;1&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;</span><br><span class="line">            child = parent;</span><br><span class="line">            parent = nodes[child].parent;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">        </span><br><span class="line">        codes[i].code[<span class="number">0</span>] = <span class="string">&#x27;\0&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">for</span> (<span class="type">int</span> j = idx - <span class="number">1</span>; j &gt;= <span class="number">0</span>; j--) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="type">int</span> len = <span class="built_in">strlen</span>(codes[i].code);</span><br><span class="line">            codes[i].code[len] = temp[j];</span><br><span class="line">            codes[i].code[len + <span class="number">1</span>] = <span class="string">&#x27;\0&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="核心操作-3"><a href="#核心操作-3" class="headerlink" title="核心操作"></a>核心操作</h3><table><thead><tr><th>操作</th><th>函数名</th><th>时间复杂度</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>建树</td><td>CreateHuffmanTree</td><td>O(n²) &#x2F; O(n log n)</td></tr><tr><td>生成编码</td><td>GenerateCodes</td><td>O(n)</td></tr><tr><td>编码</td><td>Encode</td><td>O(L)</td></tr><tr><td>解码</td><td>Decode</td><td>O(L)</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="应用场景-1"><a href="#应用场景-1" class="headerlink" title="应用场景"></a>应用场景</h3><table><thead><tr><th>应用</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>文件压缩</td><td>ZIP、JPEG、MP3</td></tr><tr><td>通信编码</td><td>高频短码</td></tr><tr><td>最优判定树</td><td>减少比较次数</td></tr></tbody></table><hr><h2 id="08-Red-Black-Tree"><a href="#08-Red-Black-Tree" class="headerlink" title="08 &#x2F; Red-Black Tree"></a>08 &#x2F; Red-Black Tree</h2><p>近似平衡的二叉搜索树，通过颜色标记与旋转维持平衡，牺牲少量查找性能换取更快的插入删除。</p><h3 id="五条性质"><a href="#五条性质" class="headerlink" title="五条性质"></a>五条性质</h3><table><thead><tr><th>编号</th><th>性质</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1</td><td>结点非红即黑</td></tr><tr><td>2</td><td>根为黑色</td></tr><tr><td>3</td><td>叶结点（NIL）为黑色</td></tr><tr><td>4</td><td>红结点的子结点均为黑（无连续红）</td></tr><tr><td>5</td><td>任一结点到叶子的所有路径黑结点数相同</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="红黑树-vs-AVL"><a href="#红黑树-vs-AVL" class="headerlink" title="红黑树 vs AVL"></a>红黑树 vs AVL</h3><table><thead><tr><th>对比项</th><th>红黑树</th><th>AVL</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>平衡条件</td><td>黑高平衡</td><td>高度差 ≤ 1</td></tr><tr><td>树高</td><td>≈ 2 log n</td><td>≈ 1.44 log n</td></tr><tr><td>查找</td><td>略慢</td><td>更快</td></tr><tr><td>插入&#x2F;删除</td><td>更快（旋转少）</td><td>较慢</td></tr><tr><td>适用场景</td><td>读写均衡</td><td>读多写少</td></tr></tbody></table><h3 id="结构体定义-4"><a href="#结构体定义-4" class="headerlink" title="结构体定义"></a>结构体定义</h3><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> RED   0</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">define</span> BLACK 1</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">RBNode</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> data;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> color;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">RBNode</span> *<span class="title">left</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">RBNode</span> *<span class="title">right</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">RBNode</span> *<span class="title">parent</span>;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125; RBNode;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    RBNode *root;</span><br><span class="line">    RBNode *nil;    <span class="comment">// 黑色哨兵</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125; RBTree;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="应用场景-2"><a href="#应用场景-2" class="headerlink" title="应用场景"></a>应用场景</h3><table><thead><tr><th>应用</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>C++ STL map &#x2F; set</td><td>底层实现</td></tr><tr><td>Java TreeMap &#x2F; TreeSet</td><td>-</td></tr><tr><td>Linux 调度器</td><td>进程管理</td></tr><tr><td>epoll</td><td>文件描述符管理</td></tr><tr><td>Nginx</td><td>定时器管理</td></tr></tbody></table><hr><h2 id="09-Complexity-Quick-Reference"><a href="#09-Complexity-Quick-Reference" class="headerlink" title="09 &#x2F; Complexity Quick Reference"></a>09 &#x2F; Complexity Quick Reference</h2><table><thead><tr><th>数据结构</th><th>访问</th><th>查找</th><th>插入</th><th>删除</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>数组</td><td>O(1)</td><td>O(n)</td><td>O(n)</td><td>O(n)</td></tr><tr><td>顺序表</td><td>O(1)</td><td>O(n)</td><td>O(n)</td><td>O(n)</td></tr><tr><td>链表</td><td>O(n)</td><td>O(n)</td><td>O(1)*</td><td>O(1)*</td></tr><tr><td>栈</td><td>O(n)</td><td>O(n)</td><td>O(1)</td><td>O(1)</td></tr><tr><td>队列</td><td>O(n)</td><td>O(n)</td><td>O(1)</td><td>O(1)</td></tr><tr><td>哈希表</td><td>N&#x2F;A</td><td>O(1)</td><td>O(1)</td><td>O(1)</td></tr><tr><td>BST</td><td>O(log n)</td><td>O(log n)</td><td>O(log n)</td><td>O(log n)</td></tr><tr><td>AVL</td><td>O(log n)</td><td>O(log n)</td><td>O(log n)</td><td>O(log n)</td></tr><tr><td>红黑树</td><td>O(log n)</td><td>O(log n)</td><td>O(log n)</td><td>O(log n)</td></tr></tbody></table><blockquote><p>*已知位置的前提下</p></blockquote><hr><h2 id="10-Learning-Path"><a href="#10-Learning-Path" class="headerlink" title="10 &#x2F; Learning Path"></a>10 &#x2F; Learning Path</h2><ol><li><strong>Foundation</strong>：顺序表 + 链表，理解堆与栈的内存模型</li><li><strong>Abstraction</strong>：掌握每种结构的核心哲学（LIFO &#x2F; FIFO &#x2F; 平衡）</li><li><strong>Implementation</strong>：手写核心操作，不依赖现成库</li><li><strong>Scenario-Driven</strong>：遇到问题时思考“哪种结构最匹配”</li><li><strong>Complexity Analysis</strong>：养成分析时间 &#x2F; 空间开销的习惯</li></ol><hr><p><em>To be continued…</em></p>]]></content>
      
      
